<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 01:16:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>币安合规人员离开金融犯罪、监控岗位</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-06/binance-compliance-staff-leave-financial-crime-monitoring-roles</link><description>当币安于 2023 年底承认美国制裁和反洗钱违规行为时，重建合规业务是交易的关键。该交易所当年早些时候聘请了美国前助理检察官诺亚·帕尔曼(Noah Perlman)担任首席合规官，领导处理制裁执行、金融犯罪监测和调查的团队。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWLtYmpqzUDg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 14:50:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-06/binance-compliance-staff-leave-financial-crime-monitoring-roles</guid></item><item><title>Strategy 第一季度未实现亏损 145 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-06/strategy-posts-14-5-billion-unrealized-loss-in-first-quarter</link><description>比特币累加器 Strategy Inc. 在第一季度录得约 145 亿美元的未实现亏损，原因是 Michael Saylor 领导的公司持有的加密货币价值下跌。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iPeMF1BmeKE0/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 12:57:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-06/strategy-posts-14-5-billion-unrealized-loss-in-first-quarter</guid></item><item><title>由于对伊朗可能停火的乐观情绪，比特币突破 70,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-06/bitcoin-ticks-up-even-as-trump-s-iran-war-threats-cloud-markets</link><description>周一，比特币自 3 月 25 日以来首次回升至 70,000 美元以上，投资者权衡有关伊朗正在寻求在持续战争中停火的报道，尽管美国总统唐纳德·特朗普升级了攻击民用基础设施的威胁。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i_9FadNWL_HQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 02:50:44 GMT</pubDate>